  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p class=\"description\"><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl137_LabelType\">Firearms you wield are especially dangerous to you and everyone nearby.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl137_LabelType\">Whenever a firearm you wield misfires or explodes, roll a d%. On a result of 1&ndash;25, the misfire or explosion is delayed; reroll the attack with a &ndash;5 penalty (penalties from the broken condition are not applied to this reroll, and a firearm that was already broken does not explode). After the reroll is resolved, apply the effects of the misfire or explosion as normal. (If the d% roll result is 26 or higher, the misfire or explosion happens as normal.) Whenever a firearm you wield explodes due to a misfire, increase the explosion&rsquo;s damage by 1d6 plus 1d6 for every 4 character levels you have.</span></p>",
